📝 PRACTICE QUESTIONS

A train 180 m long crosses a pole at 20 m/s. Find time.

A train 150 m long crosses a 100 m platform at 25 m/s. Find time.

Two trains 120 m and 80 m cross each other at 40 m/s combined speed. Find time.

A train 200 m long moves at 25 m/s. Time to cross pole?

Two trains move at 70 km/h and 50 km/h opposite directions. Find relative speed.
